				If you are only making the character to get the stien, make a level 8 DE ench instead.<BR>
<BR>
THis way you can use your illusion human or halfling to get all the basic parts of the<BR>
quest, and will be able to do the Oggok part without illusion, just alliance will do it <BR>
for you.<BR>
<BR>
A level 15 bard can do the quest with a Mask of Deception and the level 12 faction song.<BR>
<BR>
Anyone can do the quest with faction work in Oggok which can be done while in wolf form, <BR>
of course for that you need a high level druid friend... relatively lower level druids who<BR>
can wolf themselves can do it though.<BR>
<BR>
I'm going to try it as a rogue shortly, as I'm almost at level 15.
